--------------------------------------------------
TOPIC 5 : MAX(ID)
--------------------------------------------------

SELECT Name
FROM Student
WHERE ID = (
    SELECT MAX(ID)
    FROM Student
);

Output:

Demet

--------------------------------------------------
TOPIC 6 : AVG()
--------------------------------------------------

SELECT *
FROM Student
WHERE Marks > (
    SELECT AVG(Marks)
    FROM Student
);

Average Marks

95 + 100 + 95 + 98 + 91 + 89 + 85
= 653

653 / 7

= 93.29

Output:

Nikitha
Tanya
Nikitha
Ates

--------------------------------------------------
Execution of Subquery

Inner Query
        ↓
Returns a Value
        ↓
Outer Query Uses That Value

Example:

SELECT AVG(Marks)
FROM Student;

↓

93.29

↓

SELECT *
FROM Student
WHERE Marks > 93.29;

